CVE-2024-34156  # encoding/gob: deeply nested structures panic
CVE-2024-34158  # go/build/constraint: deeply nested expressions panic
CVE-2024-45336  # net/http: sensitive headers cross-domain redirect
CVE-2024-45341  # crypto/x509: IPv6 zone IDs bypass URI constraints
